{{for|the musician, the inventor of the bazantar|Mark Deutsch (musician)}}
'''Mark Deutch''' ({{lang-ru|Марк Дейч}}, also transliterated as '''Mark Deutsch''', '''Mark Deich''' and '''Mark Deitch'''; 26 January 1945 &ndash; 2 May 2012) was a [[Russia]]n journalist and columnist for ''[[Moskovskij Komsomolets]]''. He became widely known while working with [[Radio Free Europe/Radio Liberty]]. He authored several books on politics.<ref>[http://www.peoples.ru/state/correspondent/deutch/ Obituary],  peoples.ru</ref><ref>[http://www.bbc.co.uk/russian/russia/2012/05/120503_mark_deitch_death.shtml Obituary], ''[[BBC]]''</ref><ref>[http://www.svoboda.org/content/article/24568943.html Obituary], ''[[Radio Liberty]]''</ref>

